label: Puerto Rico Daily Sun
title: Puerto_Rico_Daily_Sun
exrest: Puerto Rico Daily Sun is the island's only daily English-language newspaper. The paper is based in San Juan, Puerto Rico. It is published seven days a week by Cooperativa Prensa Unida. It succeeded the "San Juan Star," which ended publication on August 29, 2008 after an almost 49-year run. Reporters had gone several weeks without being paid. The newspaper closed by the end of 2011.
